title: Counter Strike 1.6: Global Offensive Edition [English]
description:
=========================================================================

Global Offensive Edition of famous game Counter-Strike 1.6


All player models, hostage models, sounds and weapons are changed to the ones from CS:GO.

CS:GO background in menu.

The game designed to look and feel identical to CS:GO (as much as possible).

This version is completely compatible with Windows 8.1.

The game has all possible security installed.

It is 100% ads free and protected from any ad binds and other harmful server cmds.

The game is immune to amx_destroy plugin (which messes up player's client).

The game supports 48 protocol.

The performance is very smooth and lags free.

You can find some best servers in "Find servers" option (top servers from gametracker.com).	

=========================================================================
Enjoy!
